/>\n<br />\n<br />\n佢話要用銀離子（Ag+)殺菌，但又唔用係將啲ionic compound溶水，而係成條銀條車入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中學化學都會話到俾你知離子唔會單存在，一定會有相反電荷嘅離子去平衡電荷。<br />\n但係佢杯水係普通蒸餾水，冇落其他chemical，唔知佢點樣令杯水有銀離子？<br />\n同埋你見到佢搞完一大輪野有啲銀色野浮係面即係話你知啲銀冇溶入水，到最後佢杯水入面根本冇幾多銀係入面。<br />\n我假設佢真係溶到入去，佢溶去嘅量一早多過佢0.1ppm，用依啲消毒你好快就會中毒，到時死得仲快過去武漢走一轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n高登見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdf08620f0a83720ba45623a5283e33e7f65d28f","tid":1871343,"uid":169071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"929f4685247d1cad63a3e02a98a7d29b7ddbd8e9","tid":1871343,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d98b7c47cb6d7d5446fc49049398d087b8b599d0","tid":1871343,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4975860d9bdc7bc2adfccff0146873515d8d8bde","tid":1871343,"uid":44171,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T11:50:22.000Z","msg":"明明殺菌能力可以比酒精勁千倍, 成本300樓下, 可以整幾L銀出黎連登仔都咁多負評, 之後成本只係蒸餾水同電<br />\n<br />\n連登好多人炒緊酒精? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T11:55:40.000Z","msg":"google 緊 係咪比酒精勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T11:57:29.000Z","msg":"《科學轉化醫學（Science Translational Medicine）》發表研究指出，在常規抗生素中加入銀，會使殺菌能力增長10倍到1000倍。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T12:00:08.000Z","msg":"殺菌唔等於消毒，<br />\n人地仲要話係抗生素加銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce446014d719babbcb5ced680e6ebd38a0618ca5","tid":1871343,"uid":13914,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T12:00:17.000Z","msg":"點樣保證到離子濃度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58819e9dc3d64aae2cefb72486ce15bdbc515c59","tid":1871343,"uid":44171,"like":0,"disl